{"title":"数字三角形第k优解","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5585","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给你一个数字三角形 求第k优解（不严格第k优）</p><p>n&lt;=50 k&lt;=50</p><p>（PS：不严格第k优表示 假如有两个相同答案的解应将其视为不相同）<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个整数n，k。</p><p>接下来n行，每行多个正整数。</p><p>数据保证均是正整数且第k优解存在。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个正整数ans表示第k优解<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【样例输入1】<br></p><p>3 1</p><p>1</p><p>2 3</p><p>4 5 6</p><p>【样例输入2】</p><p>5 2<br></p><p>13</p><p>11 8</p><p>12 7 26</p><p>6 14 15 8</p><p>12 7 13 24 11</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【样例输出1】</p><p>10<br></p><p>【样例输出2】</p><p>79<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>n&lt;=50 k&lt;=50</p><p>感谢cdx神犇提供原题目及灵感</p><p>0&lt;=数字三角形中的数&lt;=100</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}